&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.github.com/en/pages/getting-started-with-github-pages/about-github-pages&#34;&gt;Changing the visibility of your GitHub Pages site - GitHub Docs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

      </description>
